Package: dma
Type: Package
Title: Distributional Mediation Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Xiao",
           family = "Liu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "xiao.liu@example.com")
Description: Implements causal mediation analysis using energy regression
    (engression) for nuisance parameter estimation. Supports natural effects,
    organic effects, randomized interventional effects, and recanting twins
    decompositions. Interventions are specified using modified treatment policies.
    Estimation follows the framework of Liu, Williams, Rudolph, and Diaz (2024)
    with engression replacing traditional machine learning for outcome regressions
    and engression-style neural networks for Riesz representer estimation.
